      <title>Japan's ruling party elects Sanae Takaichi as leader, likely to become first female PM</title>
      <author>The Associated Press</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/10/04/g-s1-92073/japans-sanae-takaichi-likely-to-become-first-female-pm</link>
